cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as entity linking and cross-lingual text analysis. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as entity linking is a sub-task of information retrieval. Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-categories. Finally, the use of multi-lingual embeddings suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
